---
title: Super-Stuffed Turkey Tacos with Lime Crema and Tomato Salsa
description: Check out these tortillas con todo: although this meal can be made with just a single pan, it still has all the works, with plenty of fillings and toppings to choose from. Although the turkey in a mildly spiced tomato sauce is the center of attention, there are other ingredients vying for the spotlight: sliced peppers, a tomato salsa, sour cream, and lime and cilantro for garnish. You and your family can enjoy it all or mix and match the different components just the way you like.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/super-stuffed-turkey-tacos-1e495710.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/super-stuffed-turkey-tacos-7904e0c6.pdf
cuisine: North America
